From: Nickel Browser Team <team@nickel-browser.org>
Date: Mon, 04 May 2026 04:33:43 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 07/10] nickel: fingerprint-protection — canvas/audio/webgl spoofing

Implement a real fingerprint protection layer by injecting subtle noise into
Canvas and AudioContext outputs, returning generic WebGL vendor/renderer
strings, and suppressing navigator.plugins/mimeTypes. All noise is seeded
per-session to keep values stable within a run.
---
 third_party/blink/renderer/modules/nickel_fingerprint/nickel_fingerprint_noise.cc | 96 ++++++++++++++
 third_party/blink/renderer/modules/nickel_fingerprint/nickel_fingerprint_noise.h  | 50 ++++++++
 third_party/blink/renderer/modules/canvas/canvas_rendering_context_2d.cc          | 22 +++
 third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webgl/webgl_rendering_context_base.cc          | 18 ++
 third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webaudio/dynamics_compressor_node.cc           | 14 ++
 third_party/blink/renderer/modules/navigator/navigator_plugins.cc                 | 20 +++
 6 files changed, 220 insertions(+)

